examples.en: I fell back and hurt my head.
I fell down and hurt my knee.
I fell and hit my head.
A vase fell off the shelf.
She fell down in a faint.
He fell flat on his face.
He fell flop on his face.
We fell into a plain talk.
I fell into a light sleep.
An apple fell to the ground.
He fell morosely on the bed.
He fell into a doze again.
